* VPC Gateway Endpoint For S3
- By default s3 use public internet to interact with ec2 we can prevent it using this endpoint services
- Two types of endpoints :

(1) Gateway
- s3 and dynamoDB
- no additional cost
- easier to setup

(2) Interface
- ideal for sevices which require more granular control over network traffic such as ec2,ssm or other services that support private link
- charge based on hours

- When we are usng s3 it is the recommended choise
- integrate seamlessly with vpc route tables and ensure efficient and secure access to s3 
